headline: Loomis Sayles Selects ICE Climate to Advance Climate Risk Integration Across Global Fixed Income & Equity Portfolios
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK & BOSTON, October 09, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced that Loomis, Sayles & Company has selected ICE Climate’s multi-asset suite of climate risk data and analytics to support its global approach to identifying, understanding and integrating financially material climate risk insights.
